It’s amazing how strong she is despite the fact that she’s lost her father AND her dog in 2 months. I cannot imagine how crappy she feels after losing two very close people in her life. And yet she still manages to smile for her fans. I know that she has a really popular YouTube so she has to move on. Rosanna, I really admire your strength and your commitment to your fans and channel, but PLEASE take an emotional break when u need it. ❤️ Although ur content is great and u still look kind of happy and recovered, we would love to see you when ur at ur best cuz I can imagine that ur dad and Cookie is something ur still trying to recover from. ❤️ love u Ro

Edit: sorry maybe crappy might not be the best word of choice but maybe just sad and depressed
